<% content_for :title, "About" %>
<h1>About Dog Breed Explorer</h1>

<p>
Dog Breed Explorer is a Ruby on Rails application that lets users browse,
search, and view information about dog breeds.
</p>

<p>
The main data source is the Dog CEO API:
<strong>https://dog.ceo/api/breeds/list/all</strong>
</p>

<p>
This API provides dog breed names. The project also uses the Faker gem to
generate sample reviews for each breed.
</p>

<h2>Database Tables</h2>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Breeds:</strong> stores dog breed names.</li>
  <li><strong>Breed Images:</strong> stores image URLs for dog breeds.</li>
  <li><strong>Reviews:</strong> stores sample reviews and ratings for each breed.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Project Features</h2>

<ul>
  <li>Browse all dog breeds</li>
  <li>Search dog breeds by name</li>
  <li>View individual breed details</li>
  <li>View reviews for each breed</li>
  <li>Pagination for large data navigation</li>
</ul>